babyanimals is an image service you can fork and deploy.

what's an image service?
----

 REQUEST       RESPONSE

POST an image  an id
GET /id        {{pic}}
GET /id?size=...    {{pic}}
GET /id?hipster=true {{pic}}

how to deploy
-------------
1. fork
2. set up on heroku and define these env vars
3. use!

